# Summary
This documentation details the Google Analytics 4 (Web) streaming integration for Amplitude Activation, which enables forwarding Amplitude events and user data to GA4 using gtag.js. The setup requires a GA4 Measurement ID and API Secret, with configuration options for mapping user properties, filtering events, and sending additional properties as GA4 parameters.

